    { id: 12350, title: "Questions 50-52", text: "Ms. Gao? I'm Hector, and this is my colleague Sergey. Thanks for meeting with us. It's a pleasure to meet you both. How can I help you? We're making some training videos for our client, FiveStar Industries. We found your advertisement in a trade publication. We need someone to choose appropriate filming sites at FiveStar's factories, and it said you have lots of experience scouting for industrial locations. Sure. I'd want to start by touring their factories. Can you schedule a time for me to do that next week? Yes, I'll call them today to arrange it." },
    { id: 12353, title: "Questions 53-55", text: "Our engineering firm has been asked to cut the corporate travel budget by twenty percent, but it won't be easy. The engineering consultants have to travel to meet with clients. Right, and they often travel on short notice. Flight arrangements made at the last minute are expensive, especially for nonstop flights. It would be cheaper if they took connecting flights. Yes, but that can take a lot of time. True. Maybe we can make up for the cost of the flights by economizing on hotels. Let's look into that." },
    { id: 12356, title: "Questions 56-58", text: "Thanks for meeting with us, Ms. Azuma. This is Scott Ajibade, one of our senior project managers. I admire your work, Ms. Azuma. Thank you. I was surprised by your invitation. I typically design jewelry, but your company's known for making computers and mobile phones. Scott's team is currently working on a smartwatch. But there's a lot of competition, as you know. We're hoping you can create a fresh design that will help our product stand out. Do you already have an idea of what the watch should look like, or are we starting from scratch? I have some preliminary sketches we can look at, but none of them seem quite right." },
    { id: 12359, title: "Questions 59-61", text: "Hi. I'd like to purchase some new carpeting. It's for the waiting room at my hair salon. We have many different styles. Are you looking for something different? Well, we get a lot of customers walking through, and our current carpeting is a light color. No matter what color you get, all our carpets are durable and can take high amounts of foot traffic. For businesses like yours, I recommend placing a protective mat near the door. That's a good idea. Also, I offer free cleaning services for a year for all purchases." },
    { id: 12362, title: "Questions 62-64", text: "I really need this coffee break. My morning meeting with my client was really challenging. What were you discussing? The project schedule. They asked us to provide the prototype design to them three weeks earlier than originally planned. Well. Then today's cup is my treat. Which one would you like? That's so nice of you! I'll go with the White Cloud Coffee. I like a little milk in mine. Good choice. So, I have some news to share with you. Did you hear about David? No, what's going on? Apparently, he's planning to retire next month." },
    { id: 12365, title: "Questions 65-67", text: "This is Bradley from Windows Galore. How can I help you? Hello! I'd like to have screens added to my windows at home. I was wondering if you would be available to stop by and take a look. I live at 42 West Third Street, by the way. OK—that's not far. Let me see. I could come any morning this week. How about in the afternoon? Hmm. I could reschedule my Tuesday afternoon appointment. I'll check and get back to you—I have your number now. And your name is? Hoffman—Claudia Hoffman. Thank you. Talk to you soon." },
    { id: 12368, title: "Questions 68-70", text: "Ms. Kwon, thank you for sending me to the upcoming robotics conference. I didn't expect an opportunity like this so soon after being hired here. It's important for you to be familiar with current robot designs. There are always new trends and technologies coming out, and I want you to stay ahead of developments in our industry. I agree. Plus, it'll give me the chance to introduce myself to potential clients. Oh, about that: here's a handout I provide to all new hires. It includes some helpful tips—especially this one. Do you have your business cards yet? Hmm. I haven't received them, but I'll call the printer today for an update." }
